'''垃圾广告软件'''（{{lang-en|Spamware}}）是一种由[[垃圾邮件|垃圾邮件]]发送者设计的[[软件|软件]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pcworld.about.com/magazine/2008p107id101769.htm |title=PC World: Spam Inc. |accessdate=2013-07-05 |archive-date=2008-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080415060709/http://pcworld.about.com/magazine/2008p107id101769.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。垃圾广告软件的种类很多，不过很可能包含以下功能：导入数以千计的地址，产生随机地址，在信息中插入欺诈性的标头，同时使用数十或数百个邮件服务，并且能利用[[开放转发|匿名转发]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oreillynet.com/pub/a/network/2005/04/07/spamflood.html |title=O'Reilly Network: Safe from the Spam Flood? |accessdate=2013-07-05 |archive-date=2013-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607140305/http://www.oreillynet.com/pub/a/network/2005/04/07/spamflood.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美国8个州，销售垃圾广告软件是非法的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.spamsights.org/ |title=Spamware Vendor List |accessdate=2013-07-05 |archive-date=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811004652/http://www.spamsights.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.spamhaus.org/sbl/sbl-rationale.html |title=Spamhaus Block List |accessdate=2013-07-05 |archive-date=2004-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041010234532/http://www.spamhaus.org/sbl/sbl-rationale.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://infoweek.bitpipe.com/detail/RES/1097086148_134.html |title=Thought Paper: Spamware |accessdate=2013-07-05 |archive-date=2004-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041205063100/http://infoweek.bitpipe.com/detail/RES/1097086148_134.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

另一种垃圾广告软件是能够搜索[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]地址并且建立[[邮件列表|邮件列表]]，利用此列表直接发送垃圾邮件或者把此列表卖给垃圾邮件发送者。

